STANEE
THE TITAN STORY
TITAN
BACK IN THE 1980s, TATA GROUP FORESAW
A FUTURE WHERE STYLE AND DESIGN COEXISTED
WITH UTILITY; WHERE A WATCH WOULD
REFLECT YOUR PERSONALITY AND FLATTER
YOUR STYLE. AND THAT'S WHERE IT ALL BEGAN.
